Package: examinr
Type: Package
Title: Online Exams in R via Interactive Shiny Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Kepplinger", , "david.kepplinger@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create online exams in R as interactive shiny documents.
  Supports different question types, including coding exercises, and
  strategies to deter cheating.
